lead_paragraph: Zimbabwe beat the West Indies by five runs on the Duckworth-Lewis method in Bulawayo on Friday to book a place in Sunday’s final of the triangular one-day international tournament against Sri Lanka.

headline.print_headline: Zimbabwe Edge Out West Indies to Reach One-Day Final
